               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Methocarbamol Tablets USP, 500 mg are light orange colored, round, film-coated tablets, engraved with 'B134' on one side and scored on the other side. They are supplied as follows:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 100 NDC 76385-123-01
       
 
  <br/>Bottles of 500 NDC 76385-123-50
      

 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Methocarbamol Tablets USP, 750 mg are orange colored, capsule shaped, film coated tablets, engraved with 'B135' on one side and plain on the other side. They are supplied as follows:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 100 NDC 76385-124-01</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 500 NDC 76385-124-50</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at controlled room temperature, between 20°C and 25°C (68°F and 77°F).
       
 
  <br/>Dispense in tight container.
      

